<div class="com-share" data-id="22124" data-title="《除了飞行夹克，你知道还有哪些经典款来自军队？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/22124/medium/22124.jpg?1454785870" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/22124.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
